# Workers Assets uploads everything under this directory. The files below are
# bf build internals or server-side imports (bundled into the Worker at build
# time), so they must NOT ship as public assets. Only the browser-facing
# *.client.js, barefoot.js, form.js and *.css are served.
#
# Uses .gitignore syntax (https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/static-assets/).
.dev/
.bfemit.json
.buildcache.json
barefoot-externals.json
components/manifest.json
*.tsx
